title: 25th Anniversary Box Set
text:
25th Anniversary Box Set is a 1993 limited edition box set by <a href="Jethro%20Tull%20%28band%29">Jethro Tull</a>. It includes some of the band's best-known compositions from 1969 to 1992, many of them previously unavailable in the versions presented here. It was the second Jethro Tull <a href="box-set">box-set</a> in five years, the first being the 3 CD/ 5 LP/ 3 Cassette "<a href="20%20Years%20of%20Jethro%20Tull">20 Years of Jethro Tull</a>".
Four CDs.
The CDs are housed in a mock cigar-box, along with a booklet featuring extensive notes and photographs, sealed with a label bearing an image of Ian Anderson.
